item.description:
Date and Time: Wednesday, Apr 19 2017, 5:30pm

Location: 8 Petty Pl, Cambridge, ON

http://www.ywcacambridge.ca/mentoring.html STEM Mentoring is about building gyrls' interest and skills in STEM through mentorship with amazing womyn who work in the STEM field! Each program is tailored to the interests of the gyrls who participate. Gyrls and their mentors have explored things like robotics and aerodynamics, gone on many field trips, and made things like edible water bottles and solar systems!

*Meets bi-weekly from Sept 21- June 14 Ages 9-13

Contact us for more information or to register: girlscentre@ywcacambridge.ca
